cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.DS, cs.SI, cs.DC 

The paper deals with improving the caching performance of content delivery networks, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also proposes a novel algorithm based on graph coloring, which falls under the category of data structures (cs.DS) and algorithms (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper discusses the performance of the proposed scheme under different cache sizes and demand distributions, which could be considered as a form of system optimization (cs.SI).
